snippet.title: Parwarish Episode 25 | Aina Asif | Samar Jafri | 1st JULY 2025 (Eng Sub) | ARY Digital Drama
snippet.description:
"Watch the latest Pakistani drama now, and make sure to subscribe for all the updates!"
‚û°Ô∏è https://bit.ly/arydigitalyt

Parwarish Episode 25 | Digitally Presented by Surf Excel , Vince Care, Mothercare &  VGOTEL | Aina Asif | Samar Jafri | Reham Rafiq | 1st JULY 2025 | ARY Digital Drama 

PARWARISH ‚Äì The most-watched Pakistani drama of the season, Parwarish is a gripping tale of generational conflict, where love becomes control and independence feels like rebellion. As parents hold tight to cultural traditions and children chase dreams of freedom, misunderstandings shake the very foundation of the family. It‚Äôs a powerful reflection of the emotional battles playing out in households across Pakistan today.


Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir:
Wali, the eldest son of Jahangir, is the emotional heart of Parwarish. Handsome, intelligent, and kind-hearted, Wali was raised in the freedom of America. He dreams of becoming a musician, but his father‚Äôs disapproval casts a long shadow. Now back in Pakistan, Wali must navigate a world where parental expectations and personal dreams collide, sparking the drama‚Äôs central conflict.

Aina Asif as Maya:
Maya, a bright and determined girl from a conservative, middle-class family, is ready to take on the world. Beautiful and self-assured, she aspires to become a doctor‚Äîa path her family supports only conditionally. Caught between love, ambition, and tradition, Maya embodies the struggle of many young women in today‚Äôs society.

Cast:
Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir
Aina Asif as Maya
Naumaan Ijaz as Jahangir
Savera Nadeem as Mahnoor
Shamim Hilaly as Dadi
Saad Zameer Fareedi
Reham Rafiq as Amal
Nazr-ul-Hasan as Shaheer
Bakhtawar Mazhar as Sadia
Nooray Zeeshan as Aania
Haleema Ali as Mashal
Arshad Mehmood  as Dada
Saman Ansari
Abul Hasan & others.

Writer: Kiran Siddiqui

Wali, the eldest son of Jahangir, is the emotional heart of Parwarish. Handsome, intelligent, and kind-hearted, Wali was raised in the freedom of America. He dreams of becoming a musician, but his father‚Äôs disapproval casts a long shadow. Now back in Pakistan, Wali must navigate a world where parental expectations and personal dreams collide, sparking the drama‚Äôs central conflict.

Aina Asif as Maya:
Maya, a bright and determined girl from a conservative, middle-class family, is ready to take on the world. Beautiful and self-assured, she aspires to become a doctor‚Äîa path her family supports only conditionally. Caught between love, ambition, and tradition, Maya embodies the struggle of many young women in today‚Äôs society.

Ho Lai Ja Ne Lerida Tara
Ho Lai Ja Ne Lerida Tara Nehade Javu Re

Ho Bangala Tara Paka Paya Na
Bangala Tara Paka Paya Na Kachi Mati Na Ghar
Naliya Na Thekana Nathi Kem Lai Javu Malak
Ho Lai Ja Ne Lerida Tara Nehade Javu Re

Ho Nanu Ek Zupadu Maru, Man Lagi Nai Taru
Sukh Sahebi Ma Mohya, Oy Ro To Haru
Ho Ho Ho Bangala Ni Mediye, Man Nathi Mohya
Vari Bethi Tamne Valam Jyarthi Me To Joya
Ho Halti Chatak Harni Ni Jem
Halati Chatak Harani Ni Jem, Harnya Halar Desh
Pag Ma Vagashe Kankariyu Tane Kem Hamjavu Re
Ho Lai Ja Ne Valam Tara Malak Ma Javu Re

Ho Prem Niswarth Taro, Bharoho Te Jityo Maro
Ek Bija Na Thaine Jivashu Aa Janmaro
Ho Ho Ho Haiya Na Re Het Aato, Khoti Nai Thay Vato
Saath Nai Chhodu Valam Jiv Bhale Jato
Ho Bar Medi Na Bangala Mare
Bar Medi Na Bangala, An Bangale Melya Madh
Hona Na Moraliya Bole Halo Mare Desh
Ae Halo Ne Hangath Lerida Deh Ma Jashu Re

snippet.title: Charity or Showbiz? | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
In this short video, we reflect on a growing concern within our churches,  are we truly giving from the heart, or are we more concerned about our name being announced in public? Too often, people give generously to the church just to gain recognition, while neglecting genuine needs like community development or council initiatives that benefit everyone.

Let‚Äôs pause and ask ourselves: Is our giving rooted in love, faith, and responsibility ‚Äî or is it driven by pride and empty tradition? True giving is quiet, sincere, and purposeful.

How to make tikhat mitachya purya | Ashadh Special Tikhat purya Recipe | How to make Ashadh special kapanya dhapate recipe
For the paste:To prepare the paste, take garlic, green chilies, cumin seeds, and carom seeds in a mixer jar and grind them to a paste.
To knead the puri dough:Now in a large mixing bowl, add wheat flour, sorghum flour, gram flour, and salt. Mix everything well.Heat the oil taken for shortening until it's very hot, and pour it over the flour mixture. First mix using a spoon, then rub it into the flour with your hands thoroughly.Now add the prepared paste, turmeric, white sesame seeds, chopped coriander, and dried fenugreek leaves. Mix well and knead into a stiff dough by adding a little water at a time.After kneading, apply a little oil on the dough and cover it for 10 minutes.
While rolling the puris:Roll one large roti (flatbread) and cut puris using a glass or tumbler, or roll small individual puris and keep ready for frying.
Frying the puris:Heat oil on medium flame. Once the oil is hot, add a few puris at a time (as many as the pan can hold). After adding, reduce the flame to medium and fry the puris well on both sides until crisp and golden.
Note:These puris are traditionally made during the month of Ashadha and served with raw mango pieces. Once cooled, they can be stored in an airtight container and will stay fresh for up to a month. They are a great option for travel or picnics.

How to make tikhat mitachya purya | Ashadh Special Tikhat purya Recipe | How to make Ashadh special kapanya dhapate recipe
For the paste:To prepare the paste, take garlic, green chilies, cumin seeds, and carom seeds in a mixer jar and grind them to a paste.
To knead the puri dough:Now in a large mixing bowl, add wheat flour, sorghum flour, gram flour, and salt. Mix everything well.Heat the oil taken for shortening until it's very hot, and pour it over the flour mixture. First mix using a spoon, then rub it into the flour with your hands thoroughly.Now add the prepared paste, turmeric, white sesame seeds, chopped coriander, and dried fenugreek leaves. Mix well and knead into a stiff dough by adding a little water at a time.After kneading, apply a little oil on the dough and cover it for 10 minutes.
While rolling the puris:Roll one large roti (flatbread) and cut puris using a glass or tumbler, or roll small individual puris and keep ready for frying.
Frying the puris:Heat oil on medium flame. Once the oil is hot, add a few puris at a time (as many as the pan can hold). After adding, reduce the flame to medium and fry the puris well on both sides until crisp and golden.
Note:These puris are traditionally made during the month of Ashadha and served with raw mango pieces. Once cooled, they can be stored in an airtight container and will stay fresh for up to a month. They are a great option for travel or picnics.

Humraaz is a unique tale of love, fate, and redemption, exploring the profound impact of a single tragic event on the lives of three individuals named Sara, Ahmer, and Saim. Sara is a vibrant and free-spirited young woman in a relationship with Ahmer. Meanwhile, Saim, a young and charming man, lives a life entirely separate from Sara and Ahmer. However, their paths cross dramatically when an unexpected tragedy occurs, deeply impacting Saim's life.

With all the evidence pointing toward her, suspicion quickly falls on Sara but she firmly denies any wrongdoing. Yet, Saim is convinced of her guilt and is determined to seek justice. As fate brings Sara, Ahmer, and Saim together in unforeseen ways, they must confront difficult truths, navigate confusion, and unravel the mystery behind the tragedy.

Dayan Episode 38 - [Eng Sub] - Mehwish Hayat - Ahsan Khan - Hira Mani - 1st July 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Dayan is a gripping story of a girl fighting for justice after enduring a series of injustices. It follows Nihaal, a young woman whose life is shattered by a tragic turn of events. The events that follow shake Nihaal to her core, drastically altering her personality. This leads Nihaal to embark on a journey to bring those responsible for ruining her life to justice.

Can Nihaal get the justice she deserves? Is Nihaal strong enough to take down the ones who wronged her? Can Nihaal handle everything life throws at her?

Dayan Episode 38 - [Eng Sub] - Mehwish Hayat - Ahsan Khan - Hira Mani - 1 Juli 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Dayan adalah kisah mencekam tentang seorang gadis yang memperjuangkan keadilan setelah mengalami serangkaian ketidakadilan. Kisah ini mengikuti Nihaal, seorang wanita muda yang hidupnya hancur oleh serangkaian peristiwa tragis. We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: The Coldest Village on Earth (10 minutes outside = Death) -71¬∞C, -96¬∞F
snippet.description:
Use the coupon code RUHI29 to buy the MyHeritage DNA kit for only $29/‚Ç¨29/¬£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH or start your family tree with a 14-day free trial.

Here is my friend's video:
Journey to the World's Coldest Village: Oymyakon at -71¬∞C https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6fyb46Z-SM
Don't forget to check out "The Ulengovs" channel: https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Thanks to MyHeritage for sponsoring this video.

Imagine a village where temperatures drop as low as -71¬∞C, -96¬∞F. Here, spending just a few extra minutes outside can lead to frostbite, the loss of a limb, or even end of life.

I‚Äôm in the coldest inhabited place on Earth, at the coldest time of the year. This is Oymyakon. Just to stay alive, I‚Äôm wearing more than 20 layers of clothing, weighing nearly 14 kilos. Stepping outside from a warm 30¬∞C home means facing a temperature drop of over 100 degrees. That‚Äôs why I‚Äôm also wearing gloves, boots, pants, and a coat, all made from reindeer fur. And even that‚Äôs not enough. And now, I‚Äôm about to show you what life is like when simply going outside becomes a battle for survival.

The cold doesn't just affect people and wild animals. It stops everything from functioning.  Phones don‚Äôt work properly and often shut down. Cars left outside freeze in just a few hours. Since the ground is always frozen, no fruits or vegetables can grow here.

We boarded a plane in Moscow, flying east for seven hours to Yakutsk. From there, we covered an 18 hour, 900 kilometer road trip. When we stepped out of the car, it felt like we were on another planet. The hairs in our nose were frozen, and we felt them prick with every breath. The dry air makes us cough uncontrollably.  

Oymyakon is home to around 800 people, spread across 1.5 square kilometers. Seeing anyone else outside is almost impossible, the village feels like it has been abandoned.

Our team that worked on this project ‚ñ∫ https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vDYIkyfFR1fayrUZOsA80xEN3X-nYhU003F1FewGCy8/edit?usp=sharing

Subscribe ‚ñ∫ https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
"Rediscovery" Series ‚ñ∫ https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL40Eh9f0PRRXcCkyKxrtRvE3tbmcKYvHr

Visiting the Fattest, Most Cigarette-Addicted and Least Visited Country üá≥üá∑ ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/eUJgq9HerDQ
Visiting the World's Hottest Place (70¬∞C, 159¬∞F) LUT DESERT ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/NhyDkHaUC8U
Visiting the World‚Äôs Most Da–øge–≥ous Road: ‚ÄúKarakoram D‚ÑÆath Road‚Äù (There are casuaIti‚ÑÆs!) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/FryCzL17YRs
Visiting the MOST AIR POLLUTED CITY in the World (Dust Hell) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/zC4saZg6sG0
Visiting the COLDEST CITY in the World (-71¬∞C, -96¬∞F) YAKUTSK / YAKUTIA ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/Fz4ZMLsPzqM
8 Crazy Experiments at -55¬∞C, -67¬∞F (The coldest city in the World: Yakutsk) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/ExoOL2lwlWE
World's Poorest Country "Burundi" (I can‚Äôt forget the things I saw) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/n0gFsHf9cIw

id.title: Desa Terdingin di Dunia (10 Menit di Luar = Kematian) -71¬∞C
id.description:
Gunakan kode kupon RUHI29 untuk membeli kit DNA MyHeritage hanya seharga $29/‚Ç¨29/¬£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH atau mulai silsilah keluarga Anda dengan uji coba gratis selama 14 hari.
Berikut adalah video teman saya:
Perjalanan ke Desa Terdingin di Dunia: Oymyakon pada suhu -71¬∞C https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6fyb46Z-SM
Jangan lupa untuk menonton saluran "The Ulengovs": https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Bayangkan sebuah desa yang suhunya turun hingga -71¬∞C, -96¬∞F. Di sini, menghabiskan beberapa menit di luar ruangan saja dapat menyebabkan radang dingin, kehilangan anggota tubuh, atau bahkan akhir hidup.

Saya berada di tempat berpenghuni terdingin di Bumi, pada waktu terdingin dalam setahun. Ini adalah Oymyakon. Agar tetap hidup, saya mengenakan lebih dari 20 lapis pakaian, yang beratnya hampir 14 kilogram. Melangkah keluar dari rumah yang hangat bersuhu 30¬∞C berarti menghadapi penurunan suhu lebih dari 100 derajat. Itu sebabnya saya juga mengenakan sarung tangan, sepatu bot, celana, dan mantel, yang semuanya terbuat dari bulu rusa kutub. Itu pun belum cukup. Dan sekarang, saya akan menunjukkan kepada Anda seperti apa kehidupan saat sekadar keluar rumah menjadi pertempuran untuk bertahan hidup.

Cuaca dingin tidak hanya memengaruhi manusia dan hewan liar. Cuaca dingin menghentikan semua fungsi. Ponsel tidak berfungsi dengan baik dan sering mati. Mobil yang ditinggal di luar membeku hanya dalam beberapa jam. Karena tanah selalu beku, tidak ada buah atau sayuran yang dapat tumbuh di sini.

Kami naik pesawat di Moskow, terbang ke timur selama tujuh jam menuju Yakutsk. Dari sana, kami menempuh perjalanan darat selama 18 jam, sejauh 900 kilometer. Saat kami keluar dari mobil, rasanya seperti berada di planet lain. Bulu hidung kami membeku, dan kami merasakannya menusuk setiap kali bernapas. Udara kering membuat kami batuk-batuk tak terkendali.

Oymyakon adalah rumah bagi sekitar 800 orang, tersebar di wilayah seluas 1,5 kilometer persegi. Hampir mustahil untuk melihat orang lain di luar, desa itu terasa seperti telah ditinggalkan.

Tim kami yang mengerjakan proyek ini: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1OOPAk_iEyW2ykhtBRo4g4X3kFq44Uny9H50L970WFoo/edit?usp=sharing

Mengunjungi KOTA PALING TERPOLUSI UDARA di Dunia (Dust Hell) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/zC4saZg6sG0
Mengunjungi KOTA TERDINGIN di Dunia (-71¬∞C, -96¬∞F) YAKUTSK / YAKUTIA ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/Fz4ZMLsPzqM

Saya pergi ke tempat-tempat unik atau bertemu orang-orang unik dan menyelidiki atau menganalisisnya dengan pendekatan yang unik. Moto saya adalah "rasa ingin tahu adalah pemandu terbaik". es.title: El pueblo m√°s fr√≠o de la Tierra (10 minutos fuera = Muerte) -71¬∞C, -96¬∞F
es.description:
Usa el c√≥digo de cup√≥n RUHI29 para comprar el kit de ADN de MyHeritage por solo $29/‚Ç¨29/¬£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH o empieza tu √°rbol geneal√≥gico con una prueba gratuita de 14 d√≠as.

No olvides visitar el canal "The Ulengovs": https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Imagina un pueblo donde las temperaturas caen hasta -71 ¬∞C (-96 ¬∞F). Aqu√≠, pasar tan solo unos minutos de m√°s al aire libre puede provocar congelaci√≥n, la p√©rdida de una extremidad o incluso la muerte.

Estoy en el lugar habitado m√°s fr√≠o de la Tierra, en la √©poca m√°s fr√≠a del a√±o. Esto es Oimiak√≥n. Solo para sobrevivir, llevo m√°s de 20 capas de ropa y peso casi 14 kilos. Salir de una casa con una temperatura c√°lida de 30 ¬∞C significa enfrentarme a una ca√≠da de temperatura de m√°s de 100 grados. Por eso tambi√©n llevo guantes, botas, pantalones y un abrigo, todo hecho de piel de reno. Y ni siquiera eso es suficiente. Y ahora, estoy a punto de mostrarles c√≥mo es la vida cuando simplemente salir se convierte en una batalla por la supervivencia.

El fr√≠o no solo afecta a las personas y a los animales salvajes. Impide que todo funcione. Los tel√©fonos no funcionan correctamente y a menudo se apagan. Los coches que se dejan a la intemperie se congelan en pocas horas. Como el suelo siempre est√° helado, aqu√≠ no crecen frutas ni verduras.

Subimos a un avi√≥n en Mosc√∫, volando hacia el este durante siete horas hasta Yakutsk. Desde all√≠, hicimos un viaje por carretera de 18 horas y 900 kil√≥metros. Al bajar del coche, nos sentimos como en otro planeta. Ten√≠amos los pelos de la nariz congelados y los sent√≠amos punzar con cada respiraci√≥n. El aire seco nos hace toser sin control.

Oimiak√≥n alberga a unas 800 personas, repartidas en 1,5 kil√≥metros cuadrados. Ver a alguien fuera es casi imposible; el pueblo parece abandonado.

en.title: The Coldest Village on Earth (10 minutes outside = Death) -71¬∞C, -96¬∞F
en.description:
Use the coupon code RUHI29 to buy the MyHeritage DNA kit for only $29/‚Ç¨29/¬£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH or start your family tree with a 14-day free trial.

Here is my friend's video:
Journey to the World's Coldest Village: Oymyakon at -71¬∞C https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6fyb46Z-SM
Don't forget to check out "The Ulengovs" channel: https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Thanks to MyHeritage for sponsoring this video.

Imagine a village where temperatures drop as low as -71¬∞C, -96¬∞F. Here, spending just a few extra minutes outside can lead to frostbite, the loss of a limb, or even end of life.

I‚Äôm in the coldest inhabited place on Earth, at the coldest time of the year. This is Oymyakon. Just to stay alive, I‚Äôm wearing more than 20 layers of clothing, weighing nearly 14 kilos. Stepping outside from a warm 30¬∞C home means facing a temperature drop of over 100 degrees. That‚Äôs why I‚Äôm also wearing gloves, boots, pants, and a coat, all made from reindeer fur. And even that‚Äôs not enough. And now, I‚Äôm about to show you what life is like when simply going outside becomes a battle for survival.

The cold doesn't just affect people and wild animals. It stops everything from functioning.  Phones don‚Äôt work properly and often shut down. Cars left outside freeze in just a few hours. Since the ground is always frozen, no fruits or vegetables can grow here.

We boarded a plane in Moscow, flying east for seven hours to Yakutsk. From there, we covered an 18 hour, 900 kilometer road trip. When we stepped out of the car, it felt like we were on another planet. The hairs in our nose were frozen, and we felt them prick with every breath. The dry air makes us cough uncontrollably.  

Oymyakon is home to around 800 people, spread across 1.5 square kilometers. Seeing anyone else outside is almost impossible, the village feels like it has been abandoned.

PARWARISH ‚Äì The most-watched Pakistani drama of the season, Parwarish is a gripping tale of generational conflict, where love becomes control and independence feels like rebellion. As parents hold tight to cultural traditions and children chase dreams of freedom, misunderstandings shake the very foundation of the family. It‚Äôs a powerful reflection of the emotional battles playing out in households across Pakistan today.


Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir:
Wali, the eldest son of Jahangir, is the emotional heart of Parwarish. Handsome, intelligent, and kind-hearted, Wali was raised in the freedom of America. He dreams of becoming a musician, but his father‚Äôs disapproval casts a long shadow. Now back in Pakistan, Wali must navigate a world where parental expectations and personal dreams collide, sparking the drama‚Äôs central conflict.

Aina Asif as Maya:
Maya, a bright and determined girl from a conservative, middle-class family, is ready to take on the world. Caught between love, ambition, and tradition, Maya embodies the struggle of many young women in today‚Äôs society.

It‚Äôs a powerful reflection of the emotional battles playing out in households across Pakistan today.


Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir:
Wali, the eldest son of Jahangir, is the emotional heart of Parwarish. Handsome, intelligent, and kind-hearted, Wali was raised in the freedom of America. He dreams of becoming a musician, but his father‚Äôs disapproval casts a long shadow. Now back in Pakistan, Wali must navigate a world where parental expectations and personal dreams collide, sparking the drama‚Äôs central conflict.

Aina Asif as Maya:
Maya, a bright and determined girl from a conservative, middle-class family, is ready to take on the world. Beautiful and self-assured, she aspires to become a doctor‚Äîa path her family supports only conditionally. Caught between love, ambition, and tradition, Maya embodies the struggle of many young women in today‚Äôs society.

snippet.description:
Step into Jethalal‚Äôs world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Bina Bread ke Crispy Bread Roll #breadroll ‚Äì Ab banayein super tasty Bread Roll Recipe bina bread ke bhi, woh bhi full crispy aur perfect tea time snack ke saath! Yeh Bread Roll Recipe thodi hatke hai, jisme bread nahi lekin texture aur crunch bilkul same milta hai. Oil

From love marriage vs arranged marriage, therapy jokes, toxic parenting, and Sonam-Raja-style honeymoon murder fears, to Parents Teacher Meetings slaps, privacy invasion, Instagram spying, and beating kids for spelling ‚Äúchummi‚Äù wrong, this episode brutally exposes what it‚Äôs like growing up with a ‚Äútraditional Indian dad.‚Äù

Whether you‚Äôre a college student, a working professional, a new-age parent, or just someone in therapy because of one ‚Äì you‚Äôll relate, and laugh out loud.

snippet.title: The Running Man | Official Trailer (2025 Movie) - Edgar Wright, Glen Powell
snippet.description:
Millions Hunt. One Runs. Everyone Watches. Watch the Official Trailer for The #RunningManMovie ‚Äì Only in theatres November 7

‚ÄãIn a near-future society, The Running Man is the top-rated show on television‚Äîa deadly competition where contestants, known as Runners, must survive 30 days while being hunted by professional assassins, with every move broadcast to a bloodthirsty public and each day bringing a greater cash reward. Desperate to save his sick daughter, working-class Ben Richards (Glen Powell) is convinced by the show‚Äôs charming but ruthless producer, Dan Killian (Josh Brolin), to enter the game as a last resort. But Ben‚Äôs defiance, instincts, and grit turn him into an unexpected fan favorite‚Äîand a threat to the entire system. As ratings skyrocket, so does the danger, and Ben must outwit not just the Hunters, but a nation addicted to watching him fall.

snippet.title: The CyberClash Is On! Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
Corrupt megacorps and freedom-fighting Renegades battle for control of a neon-soaked dystopia! The CyberClash is on! Gear up with cybernetic Hero Skins and take a side in this battle of might and metal. Explore the Cyber Scenery and add some holographic hijinks to your Home Village. A whole host of epic Events and offers await this Season! 

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

snippet.description:
üé∂ MANGLI RENUKA YELLAMMA | BONALU SONG 2025 üéâ
Celebrate the divine power of Renuka Yellamma with this energetic Bonalu 2025 anthem! Sung by the sensational Mangli and composed by the dynamic Suresh Bobbili, this song is a tribute to Telangana‚Äôs rich folk culture and the fierce goddess worshipped across the region.

Feel the spiritual energy rise as beats, devotion, and traditional Telangana folk vibes come alive in this electrifying song.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Every Indian In Hotels   | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
The highlight of every vacation or trip is staying in hotels with family , friends , siblings or our cousin gang . Re-live every moment of staying in hotels during holidays .  

Link for Himalaya Turmeric Serum : https://amzn.to/3T6Xeda

This video is all about Every Indian in Hotels , relive the hilarious, relatable, and unforgettable moments we all go through while staying in hotels during holidays. From breakfast buffet , middle class family staying in 5 star hotel for vacation , indian mom excited about everything , enjoying free amenities , free toiletries , making free chai coffee in hotel room , bhai behen mummy papa enjoying bhujia biscuit snacks , big families in resorts , road trip to goa with friends , ordering food from outside hotel , room tour , playing pool , going to hotel gym , gossiping , honeymoon couple in bali , language struggle , ordering expensive hotel food , sisters in thailand , chilled ac struggles in hotel rooms , or just a staycation , some friends saving money staying in cheap hotel , some in air bnb , home stay , resorts ‚Äî if you know, you know! üòÇ
Relish and Relive your vacation Memories of every hotel ever

snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle | MAIN TRAILER
snippet.description:
Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle is only in Movie Theatres September 12 ‚öîÔ∏è https://demonslayer-movie.com

Tanjiro Kamado ‚Äì a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon.

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps‚Äô highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.

The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons‚Äô stronghold ‚Äì the Infinity Castle. And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

snippet.title: NEW MOB AND GEAR IN THE NEXT GAME DROP!
snippet.description:
Clink-clonk! What‚Äôs that sound, you ask? It‚Äôs a new friend who will hang around your base and keep your chests tidy! Get reacquainted with the copper golem, brought back from a previous mob vote to organize your inventory and delight you with its overwhelming cuteness. 

Join Agnes Larsson (inside an actual copper mine!), Matthew Clohessy, and Eric Grimsborn as they give us the scoop on making the copper golem and its copper chest as well as the copper gear! Why are they SO excited about copper tools? And did Agnes remember to place torches as she ventured into the mine? Keep watching and find out! 

Test the copper golem, chest, and gear and send us your feedback at bugs.mojang.com!

Go to www.falugruva.se to learn more about the mine Agnes visited!

* Vibrant Visuals graphics upgrade is currently only available for compatible Minecraft: Bedrock Edition devices. Coming in the future to Java Edition.

Note: we accidentally featured a mis-colored glowberry in this Dev Diary. Whoops! Though we have been known to sneak secrets into our videos, this is an actual mistake and doesn't hint at anything. We are working on game drops packed with new features, but re-colored glowberries aren't one of them. Apologies to fans of cave fruit!
